## Cleanup / teardown

When project complete or user asks to stop:
1. Final tracker update (`current_milestone` ‚Üí "complete" or "halted")
2. Final dashboard render
3. Shut down each teammate
4. Run **`team-forge:teardown`** ‚Äî it archives the ledger to the KB, prunes worktrees, removes
   this launcher skill + its trigger + the dispatch profiles, and classifies the rest as durable
   (keep) vs ephemeral (remove). "Complete" is not "cleaned up" ‚Äî teardown is the explicit close.
